Class Richard Gidcumb Mi.  80  We want to thank everyone for coming for taking part in the 2007 World Championship and making it a great sucess. We also want to give a special thanks to our Judges and Spotters, Rick Posey, Sam Byrd, Jim Pickett, Nicky Peppers, Derek Minor and Russ Curtis for the great job they did. Also want to give a special thanks to Victoria Rodgers for the great job at the score table that she always does. Thank everyone.  Jesse Rodgers
